OL,3,CQuarter of adults set to buy pre-loved
OL,4,Cgifts for children this Christmas
OL,6,FA quarter of adults in the UK are set
OL,7,Fto buy pre-loved gifts for children
OL,8,Fthis Christmas, according to Oxfam.
OL,10,FA study of 2,000 adults who celebrate
OL,11,Fthe festive season found a quarter
OL,12,F(24%) will likely buy pre-loved gifts
OL,13,Ffor children this year ` with the most
OL,14,Fpopular gifts being pre-loved books
OL,15,F(34%), toys (30%) and board games
OL,16,F(17%).
