OL,3,CQuarter of adults set to buy pre-loved
OL,4,Cgifts for children this Christmas
OL,6,FThe YouGov survey, carried out on
OL,7,Fbehalf of Oxfam, found that helping
OL,8,Fthe planet and saving money are key
OL,9,Fdrivers for sustainable shoppers this
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FMore than half of Brits set to buy pre-
OL,13,Floved gifts said the main reason is
OL,14,Fbecause it is better for the
OL,15,Fenvironment (57%) and cheaper than
OL,16,Fbuying new (51%).
OL,18,FOxfam's retail trading director Lorna
OL,19,FFallon said: "Shopping second-hand is
OL,20,Fsuch a wonderful way of celebrating
OL,21,FChristmas, especially with children.
