OL,6,FBritish people also think pre-loved
OL,7,Fpresents are more thoughtful, with one
OL,8,Fin four (27%) saying the main reason
OL,9,Fthey would likely buy a second-hand
OL,10,Fgift at Christmas is because it will
OL,11,Fbe "unique".
OL,13,FSix in 10 (60%) say they would feel
