OL,6,FFor adults, the most popular choice of
OL,7,Fpre-loved gift is books, with nearly
OL,8,Fhalf (49%) saying they would likely
OL,9,Fgift second-hand books this Christmas,
OL,10,Fwhile a quarter (24%) said they would
OL,11,Flikely gift pre-loved clothes.
OL,13,FMs Fallon said: "Christmas shopping
OL,14,Fcan feel overwhelming at times, but
OL,15,Fsecond-hand shopping offers an
OL,16,Falternative where you can find a real
OL,17,Frange of thoughtful, unique gifts
OL,18,Fwhich help reduce waste and conserve
OL,19,Fprecious resources at the same time.
